.NET Framework 3.5.name: Drone

params.value: We pass in a Gameobject for the drone -- this will be phased out and the new drone_obj gameObject will be instantiated in this method

methods.name: AddWaypoint(Waypoint newWaypoint)
methods.summary: Use this to add a new Waypoint to the end of the drone's path

params.value: The Waypoint which is to be added to the end of path

methods.name: DeleteWaypoint(Waypoint deletedWaypoint)
methods.summary: Use this to remove a waypoint from the path and from the scene

params.value: The waypoint which is to be deleted

methods.name: InsertWaypoint(Waypoint newWaypoint, Waypoint prevWaypoint)
methods.summary: Use this to insert a new waypoint into the path (between two existing waypoints)

params.value: The Waypoint which is to be added to the path
The existing Waypoint just before the one which is to be added to the path

methods.syntax: public void InsertWaypoint(Waypoint newWaypoint, Waypoint prevWaypoint)

methods.name: Select()
methods.summary: Use this to change which drone is selected in the world. This also changes all drone aura materials so this drone is the only yellow one.
